msgstr "以下のCIがグリーンかどうかを確認します。"

#: ../../../development/release.md:48
msgid "* [GitHub Actions][github-actions-pgroonga]"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../development/release.md:50
msgid ""
"## Check whether we can build packages on `nightly` repository of "
"launchpad.net"
msgstr "## launchpad.netの `nightly` リポジトリーでビルドができるか確認"

#: ../../../development/release.md:52 ../../../development/release.md:100
msgid "For Ubuntu, packages are provided by PPA on launchpad.net."
msgstr "Ubuntuの場合、パッケージはlaunchpad.netのPPAで提供されます。"

#: ../../../development/release.md:54
msgid ""
"We have [nightly][launchpad-groonga-nightly] and [ppa][launchpad-groonga-ppa] repositories on launchpad.net.\n"
"`nightly` is for testing, and `ppa` is for distributing."
msgstr ""
"launchpad.netには[nightly][launchpad-groonga-nightly]リポジトリーと[ppa][launchpad-groonga-ppa]リポジトリーがあります。\n"
"`nightly` はテスト用で、 `ppa` は配布用です。"

#: ../../../development/release.md:57
msgid ""
"We should test whether we can build packages for Ubuntu on the `nightly` "
"repository before tagging."
msgstr "タグを打つ前に、 `nightly` リポジトリーを使って、Ubuntu向けのビルドができるかどうかを確認します。"

#: ../../../development/release.md:59
msgid "* Create archive file and upload to the `nightly` repository"
msgstr "アーカイブファイルの作成、 `nightly` リポジトリーへのアップロード"

#: ../../../development/release.md:61
msgid ""
"  ```console\n"
"  $ rake dist\n"
"  $ rake package:ubuntu DPUT_CONFIGURATION_NAME=groonga-ppa-nightly DPUT_INCOMING=\"~groonga/ubuntu/nightly\" LAUNCHPAD_UPLOADER_PGP_KEY=xxxxxxx\n"
"  ```"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../development/release.md:66 ../../../development/release.md:108
msgid "* Check the build result"
msgstr "* ビルド結果の確認"

#: ../../../development/release.md:68
msgid ""
"  When uploading packages into the `nightly` repository is succeeded, \n"
"  a package build process is executed on launchpad.net.\n"
"  Then the build result is notified via E-mail if the build fails."
msgstr ""
"  `nightly` リポジトリーへのアップロードが成功すると、パッケージのビルド がlaunchpad.net上で実行されます。\n"
"  パッケージのビルドに失敗した場合、ビルド結果がメールで通知されます。"

#: ../../../development/release.md:72
msgid "## Tagging for the release"
msgstr "## リリース用にタグを打つ"

#: ../../../development/release.md:74
msgid ""
"```console\n"
"$ rake tag\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

