#: ../../../development/release.md:166
msgid "## Update the repository"
msgstr "## リポジトリーの更新"

#: ../../../development/release.md:168
msgid "We update the repository in the following steps."
msgstr "以下の手順でリポジトリーを更新します。"

#: ../../../development/release.md:170
msgid "Clone the packages.groonga.org repository:"
msgstr "packages.groonga.orgリポジトリーをクローンします。"

#: ../../../development/release.md:172
msgid ""
"```console\n"
"$ git clone git@github.com:groonga/packages.groonga.org.git\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../development/release.md:176
msgid "Update repositories for Debian GNU/Linux and CentOS:"
msgstr "Debian GNU/LinuxとCentOS用にリポジトリーを更新します。"

#: ../../../development/release.md:178
msgid ""
"```console\n"
"$ cd packages.groonga.org\n"
"$ rake apt\n"
"$ rake yum\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../development/release.md:184
msgid "### Update Docker images"
msgstr "### Dockerイメージの更新"

#: ../../../development/release.md:186
msgid ""
"We update PGroonga's Docker images of [Docker Hub][pgroonga-docker-hub]."
msgstr "[Docker Hub][pgroonga-docker-hub]のPGroongaのDockerイメージを更新します。"

#: ../../../development/release.md:188
msgid ""
"Clone [PGroonga's Docker repository][pgroonga-docker-repository] and update "
"Dockerfiles in tha repository."
msgstr ""
"[PGroongaのDockerリポジトリー][pgroonga-docker-"
"repository]をクローンし、リポジトリーの中のDockerfileを更新します。"

#: ../../../development/release.md:190
msgid ""
"Here is an example for the case that the PGroonga version is `2.4.1`, and "
"the Groonga version is `12.0.9`."
msgstr "以下は、PGroongaのバージョンが `2.4.1` 、Groongaのバージョンが `12.0.9` の場合の例です。"

#: ../../../development/release.md:192
msgid ""
"```\n"
"$ mkdir -p ~/work/pgroonga\n"
"$ rm -rf ~/work/pgroonga/docker.clean\n"
"$ git clone --recursive git@github.com:pgroonga/docker.git ~/work/pgroonga/docker.clean\n"
"$ cd ~/work/pgroonga/docker.clean\n"
"$ ./update.sh 2.4.1 12.0.9 #Automatically update Dockerfiles and commit changes and create a tag.\n"
"$ git push --tags\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../development/release.md:201
msgid "You have to specify the latest versions."
msgstr "作業時には最新のバージョンを指定してください。"

#: ../../../development/release.md:203
msgid ""
"After you check [GitHub Actions of the PGroonga's Docker repository][github-"
"actions-pgroonga-docker] are succeeded, push tag to remote."
msgstr ""
"[PGroongaのDockerリポジトリーのGithub Actions][github-actions-pgroonga-"
"docker]が成功しているのを確認したら、タグをpushします。"

#: ../../../development/release.md:205
msgid ""
"```console\n"
"$ git push --tags\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../development/release.md:209
msgid ""
"[GitHub Actions of the PGroonga's Docker repository][github-actions-"
"pgroonga-docker] automatically update the PGroonga's docker images of "
"[Docker Hub][pgroonga-docker-hub] after you push the tag."
msgstr ""
"タグをpushすると、[PGroongaのDockerリポジトリーのGithub Actions][github-actions-pgroonga-"
"docker]が[Docker Hub][pgroonga-docker-hub]のPGroongaのDockerイメージを自動で更新します。"

